EN: His weight exceeds the standard weight.

ZH: 她最近在减肥，体重已经下降了。
EN: She has been losing weight recently and her weight has already dropped.

ZH: 他每周都在测量自己的体重。
EN: He measures his weight every week.

ZH: 体重过轻可能会导致健康问题。
EN: Being underweight can lead to health issues.

ZH: 训练之后，我感觉我的体重有所增加。
EN: After training, I feel that my weight has increased.

ZH: 我们的体重不断波动。
EN: Our weight keeps fluctuating.

ZH: 她体重恢复正常后，开始感到更健康了。
EN: After her weight returned to normal, she started feeling healthier.

ZH: 他们定期检查体重以保持健康。
EN: They regularly check their weight to maintain health.

ZH: 她的体重稳定在120磅左右。
EN: Her weight has stabilized around 120 pounds.

ZH: 体重在一定程度上取决于饮食和锻炼。
EN: Weight to some extent depends on diet and exercise.

ZH: 他的体重正常，没有必要担心。
EN: His weight is normal, there is no need to worry.

ZH: 减肥并不只是为了减少体重，更重要的是保持健康。
EN: Losing weight is not just about reducing weight, it is more important to maintain health.

ZH: 她已经达到理想的体重了。
EN: She has reached her ideal weight.

ZH: 体重不是健康的唯一标志。
EN: Weight is not the only indicator of health.

ZH: 我可以感受到我的体重对我的运动性能产生了影响。
EN: I can feel that my weight is affecting my athletic performance.

ZH: 控制体重是健康生活的关键。
EN: Managing weight is crucial for a healthy lifestyle.

ZH: 他的体重减少了二十公斤。
EN: He lost twenty kilograms in weight.

ZH: 饮食对体重控制至关重要。
EN: Diet is crucial for weight control.

ZH: 她的体重持续增加，需要寻求医生的建议。
EN: Her weight continues to increase and she needs to seek advice from a doctor.
